---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'OpenAI 发布 GPT-5.5 迄今最智能的模型';
const description = 'OpenAI 发布 GPT-5.5，在编码、知识工作和科学研究方面实现重大飞跃，同时保持与 GPT-5.4 相同的响应速度。';
---

<Layout 
  title={title}
  description={description}
  type="article"
  publishedTime="2026-04-23"
  tags={["OpenAI", "GPT-5.5", "AI-Model", "Coding", "Agentic-AI"]}
>
  <article class="article-content">
    <h1 class="lang-content lang-zh active">OpenAI 发布 GPT-5.5 迄今最智能的模型</h1>
    <h1 class="lang-content lang-en">OpenAI Releases GPT-5.5 Its Smartest Model Yet</h1>
    
    <time datetime="2026-04-23">2026-04-23</time>
    
    <div class="lang-content lang-zh active">
      <p>OpenAI 发布 GPT-5.5，这是其迄今最智能、最直观的模型。该模型在编码、知识工作和科学研究方面实现重大飞跃，同时保持与 GPT-5.4 相同的响应速度。</p>
      
      <p>GPT-5.5 在 Terminal-Bench 2.0 上达到 82.7% 的准确率，在 SWE-Bench Pro 上达到 58.6%，在 Expert-SWE（内部评估）上超越 GPT-5.4。更重要的是，它在完成相同任务时使用的 token 更少，效率显著提升。</p>
      
      <p>该模型在科学研究和数学领域也表现出色。在 GeneBench 遗传学数据分析评估上达到 25%，在 FrontierMath Tier 4 上达到 35.4%，甚至帮助发现了一个关于 Ramsey 数的新数学证明。</p>
      
      <p>GPT-5.5 现已向 Plus、Pro、Business 和 Enterprise 用户推出，API 版本即将上线。定价为每百万输入 token 5 美元，输出 token 30 美元。</p>
      
      <p><a href="https://openai.com/index/introducing-gpt-5-5/" target="_blank">阅读原文</a></p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="lang-content lang-en">
      <p>OpenAI released GPT-5.5, its smartest and most intuitive model yet. The model achieves major breakthroughs in coding, knowledge work, and scientific research while maintaining the same response latency as GPT-5.4.</p>
      
      <p>GPT-5.5 reaches 82.7% accuracy on Terminal-Bench 2.0, 58.6% on SWE-Bench Pro, and outperforms GPT-5.4 on Expert-SWE internal evaluation. More importantly, it uses significantly fewer tokens to complete the same tasks, marking a substantial efficiency improvement.</p>
      
      <p>The model also excels in scientific research and mathematics. It achieves 25% on GeneBench genetics data analysis, 35.4% on FrontierMath Tier 4, and even helped discover a new mathematical proof about Ramsey numbers.</p>
      
      <p>GPT-5.5 is now rolling out to Plus, Pro, Business, and Enterprise users, with API access coming soon. Pricing is $5 per million input tokens and $30 per million output tokens.</p>
      
      <p><a href="https://openai.com/index/introducing-gpt-5-5/" target="_blank">Read the full article</a></p>
    </div>
    
    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to articles</a>
  </article>
</Layout>
